hadiths[67]{hadithnumber,text}:
3669,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab sharab ki hurmat nazil hui to us waqt ye paanch chizon se tayyar hoti thi yani angoor , khajoor , shehad , gehun aur jo se. aur sharab ( khumr ( se murad her wo chiz hai jo aql par parda dal dey. aur teen baaton ke mutalliq meri khahish ye rahi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki wazahat kerney se pehley ham se juda na huey hotey . dada ki virasat, kalala ka hissa aur sood ke baaz masayel ."
3670,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq aata hai ke jab sharab ki hurmat nazil hui to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ! sharab ke baarey mein hamen saaf saaf hukm bayan farma dijiye. chunanche sura baqara ki ye aayat nazil hui ( يَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنِ الْخَمْرِ . . .) '' (aey Nabi ! ( log aap se khamr ( sharab (aur joey ke mutalliq daryaft kartey hain, to keh diijiye ke un dono mein bahut bada gunah hai) aur logon ke liye (kuch) faeyda bhi hai, lekin un dono ka gunah unke faaedey se bahut ziyada hai.'') phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya gaya aur unhen ye aayat sunai gaee. unhoney kaha : aey Allah ! hamen khamr ke baarey mein saaf saaf hukm bayan farma dey. chunanche sura nisaa ki ye aayat nazil hui ( يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا لَا تَقْرَبُوا . . .) ''aey emaan walo ! tum us waqt Namaz ke qarib na jao jab tum nashay mein ho.'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka manadi Namaz ki iqaamat ke waqt aelan kya karta tha : khabrdar ! koi shakhs nashay ki haalat mein Namaz ke qarib na aaye . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney ye aayat padhi gaee to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ! hamen sharab ke baarey mein saaf saaf hukm bayan farma dein. chunanche sura maayda ki ye aayat nazil hui ( فَهَلْ أَنْتُمْ . . .) (yaqinan khamr haram hai aur shetani aamaal mein se hai) kya tum un se baaz aatey ho?'' to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir ham baaz aa gaey."
3671,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik Ansari ne unki aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ki dawat ki aur unhen sharab pilai aur ye waqia hurmat sharab se pehley ka hai. chunanche Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki namaze-Maghrib mein imaamat karaai aur Sura Kafirun ki qirat kerney lagey magar usmein unsey ghalati ho gaee. chunanche ye hukm nazil hua ( لَا تَقْرَبُوا الصَّلَاةَ وَأَنْتُمْ . . .) '' nashay ki haalat mein Namaz ke qarib mat jao, yahan tak ke janney lago ke tum kya keh rahey ho.''"
3672,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke aayaat kareema ( يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا لَا تَقْرَبُوا الصَّلَاةَ وَأَنْتُمْ سُكَارَى . . .) aur ( يَسْأَلُونَكَ عَنِ الْخَمْرِ وَالْمَيْسِرِ قُلْ فِيهِمَا إِثْمٌ كَبِيرٌ وَمَنَافِعُ لِلنَّاسِ . . .) un dono ko ( إِنَّمَا الْخَمْرُ وَالْمَيْسِرُ وَالْأَنْصَابُ . . .) ne mansookh kar diya hai.
3673,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke main Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein ehle majlis ko sharab pila raha tha ke sharab ki hurmat ka hukm nazil ho gaya. aur us din hamari sharab '' fazeekh '' ( kachchi khajoor se tayyar ki hui sharab) thi. eik aadmi hamarey paas aaya aur usney kaha : tehqiq sharab haram kar di gaee hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke manadi ne aelan bhi kar diya. pas ham ne kaha : ye shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki janib se aelan kar raha hai.
3674,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne sharab, uskey peeney waley, pilaney waley, bechney waley, kharidney waley, angoor nichodne waley, nichudwaane waley, uskey uthaney waley aur jiski taraf uthai ja rahi ho, un sab par lanat ki hai.''"
3675,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke yatimon ko wirsey mein sharab mili hai. aapney farmaya : ''usey baha do (aur zaya kar do.) unhoney kaha : kya main us se sirka na bana lun? aapney farmaya : '' nahin .''
3676,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' angoor se sharab hai, khajoor se sharab hai, shehad se sharab hai, gehun se sharab hai aur jo se bhi sharab hai.''"
3677,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''bila-shuba angoor ke sharbat sey, kishmish, khajoor, gehun, jo aur makai se sharab banti hai, aur main tumhen her nasha aawar se mana karta hun.''"
3678,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sharab un do darakhton se hai yani khajoor aur angoor se. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke sanad ke raawi abu-Kaseer al-Ghabri ka naam Yazid bin Abdur-Rehman bin Ghufela Sehmi hai. baaz ne ( أذينة ( kaha hai lekin) غفيلة ( hi sahih hai.
3679,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her nasha aawar cheez khamr ( sharab ( hai aur her nasha aawar haram hai, aur jo shakhs is haalat par mar gaya ke wo sharab peeta tha to wo aakhirat mein nahin piyega.''"
3680,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her wo chiz jo aql par parda dal dey wo khumr (sharab) hai, aur her nasha aawar haram hai, aur jisney koi nasha aawar chiz istimal ki uski chaalis din ki namazein kaat li jaeyngi. agar usney tauba ki tu Allah uski tauba qubul farma lega, agar usney chauthi baar peeney ka iaada kya to Allah par ye haq hoga ke usey .) طينة الخبال ( pilaey. puchha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( طينة الخبال ( se kya murad hai? aapney farmaya : ''ye jahannamiyon ki peep hai. aur jisney kisi kam umr ko sharab pila di jisey halal haram ki tamiz na thi tu Allah par haq hoga ke usey ( طينة الخبال ( yani jahannamiyon ki peep pilaey .''"
3681,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis chiz ki kaseer miqdaar nasha aawar ho uski qaleel miqdaar bhi haram hai.''
3682,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bitaa ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : '' her wo mashrub jo nasha aawar ho haram hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine Yazid bin Abde-Rabba al-Jarjisi par hadees ki qirat ki . iski sanad ye thi : Muhammad bin Harab ne zubaidi sey, unhoney Zohri se apni sanad ke sath ye hadees riwayat ki . us mein mazeed hai. bitaa se murad shehad ki sharab hai jo ke ehle Yamen istimal kya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, kehtey they ( La-ilaah-illallah ( jarjisi kaisa ajeeb , moatabar aur bharosey wala aadmi tha. ehle-Hims mein us jaisa koi aadmi nahin tha."
3683,"Hazrat Delam Himyari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham sard ilaqey ke log hain, hamen mashaqqat bharey kaam karna padta hai, ham us gehun se eik mashrub banatey hain jis se apney kaam mein taqat hasil kartey aur sardi ka difaa kartey hain. aapney daryaft farmaya : ''kya ye mashrub nasha deta hai? ''maine kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : '' to us se bacho .'' maine arz kya ke log to usey nahin chodengey, aapney farmaya : ''agar wo na chhoden to us par un se qitaal karo.''"
3684,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine shehad ki sharab ke mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maloom kya to aapney farmaya : '' yehi bitaa hai.'' maine kaha ke jo aur makai se bhi nabeez (nasha aawar mashrub) banaya jata hai. aapney farmaya : ''ye Muzir hai.'' phir aapney farmaya : ''apni qom ko bata dey ke her nasha aawar chiz haram hai.''
3685,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab, juey, saarangi aur Ghabira se mana farmaya hai, aur farmaya : '' her nasha aawar chiz haram hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-salam abu-Ubaid ne kaha ke ''Ghubera'' makai juwar waghera se banai janey wali sharab hai jo ehle-Habsha banatey hain."
3686,Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne her nasha aawar aur susti laney (sun kar denay) wali cheezon se mana farmaya hai.
3687,ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : '' her nasha aawar chiz haram hai jis chiz ka bada piyala nasha aawar ho to uska eik chullu bhi haram hai.''
3688,"Malik bin abi Maryam kehtey hain ke Abdur-Rehman bin Ghanam (Rahimahullah) aaye aur tilaa (angoor ke sheerey ko paka liya jaey yahan tak ke do hissey khushk ho jaey aur eik hissey baqi reh jaey to usey tilaa kehtey hain) ka zikr hua to unhoney kaha : Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' (eik waqt aaeyga ke) meri ummat ke kuch log sharab piyengey aur uska naam kuch aur rakh lengey.''"
3689,Janab Abu-Mansoor Haris bin Mansoor kehtey hain : maine Janab Sufiyan Sauri (Rahimahullah) se suna jabkey un se baada ke mutalliq sawal kya gaya to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke kuch log sharab piyengey aur uska naam kuch aur rakh lengey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya ke Sufiyan Sauri (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke baada fasiq logon ka mashrub hai.
3690,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr aur Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se riwayat hai, un dono ne kaha : ham gawahi detey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kadu ke bartan (tonba), sabz (hara) rang ka bartan jis mein raughan mila liya jata tha, raughane-zuft lagey bartan aur chobi bartan se mana farmaya hai.''"
3691,"Janab Saeed bin Jubair (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se suna, wo bayan kar rahey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghadey ki nabeez haram farmai hai. Saeed kehtey hain ke main unki baat se ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghadey ki nabeez haram farmaai hai, ghabra kar nikal aaya aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas pahuncha. maine puchha : kya aapney ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki baat suni hai? unhoney kaha : wo kya hai? maine kaha : wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghadey ki nabeez haram farmai hai. unhoney kaha ke sach kaha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghadey ki nabeez haram ki hai. maine puchha ke ghadey se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha ke her wo bartan jo mitti se bana ho."
3692,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke qabeela abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham qabeela Rabeea ke log hain. hamarey aur aap ke darmiyan Muzar ke kuffar rukawat hain. ham aap ke paas sirf hurmat ke mahinon mein aa saktey hain. lihaza aap hamen aisi baat farma diijiye jisey ham pakad lein aur apney peechey walon ko bhi uski dawat den. aapney farmaya : ''main tumhen chaar baaton ka hukm deta hun aur chaar se mana karta hun. Allah par emaan aur (La-ilaah-illallah) ki shahadat aur aapney apney haath se eik adad ki gireh banai (eik ka ishara kya) . . . Musaddad ne sirf emaan billah ka zikr kya. . .phir aapney unhen uski wazahat farmaai ke is baat ki gawahi dene ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur Muhammad Allah ke Rasool hain, Namaz qaaim karna, Zakat dena aur jo ghanimat tumhen hasil ho us mein se paanchwan hissey ada karna. aur main tumhen kadu ke bartan (taunbey), sabz (hara) bartan jis par kisi tarah ka raughan mala gaya ho, raughane-zuft lagey bartan aur raughane-qeer lagey bartan se mana karta hun. ibne-Ubaid ne (muqeer) ki bajaey (naqeer) (lakdi ko khokhla karkey banaya hua bartan) ka lafz kaha . jabkey Musaddad ne naqeer aur muqeer kaha, unhoney muzaffat ka zikr nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke sanad mein mazkur abu-Jamra ka naam nasar bin Imran Zabee hai."
3693,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafad abdul-Qais ke logon se farmaya : ''main tumhen lakdi ke khudey huey bartan, raughane-zuft lagey bartan, sabz (hara) rang ke raughan miley huey bartan aur kadu ke bartan (taunbey) se mana karta hun aur badi mushk se bhi jis ko ooper se kaata gaya ho aur pendey ki taraf se surakh na hon mana karta hun, lekin apney mishkeezey se piya karo aur phir uska munh baandh diya karo.'' (yani us mein nabeez banaya karo .)"
3694,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhu) se wafad abdul-Qais ke qissey mein marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney puchha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! ham kin bartanon mein piya karen. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chamdey ke mishkeezey istimal karo jinkey munhon par taaga lapet kar unhen band kya jata hai.''
3695,"Abul-Qamoos Zaid bin Ali se riwayat hai usney wafad abdul-Qais ke eik aadmi se naqal kya jo us wafad mein shareek tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua tha. . . (raawi hadees) Auf ka khayal hai ke uska naam Qais bin Noman tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''lakdi ke bartan, raughan zuft waley bartan, kadu ke bartan (taunbey) ya sabz (harey) raughan miley bartan mein mat piyo, balke chamdey ke mishkeezey mein piyo jiska munh baandha jata hai, agar nabeez mein shiddat aa jaey (tursh ho jaey) to uski shiddat ko pani dal kar khatam kar lo , agar wo khatam na ho to usey baha do .''"
3696,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke wafad abdul-Qais ke logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham kis mein piyen ? aapney farmaya : '' kadu ke bartan ( taunbey ( , tarkol lagey bartan aur lakdi ke bartan mein mat piyo , apney mishkeezon mein nabeez banaya karo.'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar mishkeezon mein hotey huey bhi us mein shiddat aa jaey to ? aapney farmaya : '' us mein mazeed pani dal liya karo.'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! to aapney teesri ya chauthii baar farmaya : ''usey baha dalo .'' phir farmaya : ''Allah taala ne mujh par haram farmaya hai ya kaha . . . haram ki gaee hai. . sharab, jua aur kooba.'' aur farmaya : ''her nasha deney wali chiz haram hai. Sufiyan Sauri kehtey hain ke maine Ali bin Bazeema sey, kooba'' ki wazahat poochhi to unhoney kaha : ''us se murad dhol hai.''"
3697,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen kadu ke bartan (taunbey) raughan lagey huey sabz (hara) bartan, lakdi ke bartan aur jo ki sharab se mana farmaya hai."
3698,"Janab Suleman bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen teen baaton se roka tha, ab main tumhen unke baarey mein hukm deta hun, maine tumhen qabron ki ziyaarat se roka tha, ab unki ziyaarat ko jaya karo, beshak unki ziyaarat mein ibrat aur nasihat hai. maine tumhen chamdon ke bartanon ke ilawa kaee bartanon mein peeney se mana kya tha, to sab qism ke bartanon mein pi saktey ho lekin koi nasha aawar chiz mat piyo. maine tumhen kaha tha ke qurbani ka gosht teen din ke baad istimal karna mana hai to ab usey kha saktey ho aur apney safaron mein us se faeyda uthao.''"
3699,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bartanon se mana farmaya to ansaar ne kaha : hamen un bartanon ke istimal se koi chaara nahin hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to phir koi harj nahin .'' ( istimal kar saktey ho.'' nichey likhi hadees mein mazeed wazahat hai.)
3700,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bartanon ka zikr farmaya. yani kadu ka bartan (tonba), raughan mila hua sabz (hara) bartan, raughan zuft laga hua bartan aur lakdi khod kar banaya janey wala bartan, to eik earaab ne kaha : (unke ilawa) hamarey paas aur koi bartan hi nahin hotey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( to phir sirf ( wohi piyo jo halal ho.'' (yani mehaz bartan se koi chiz halal ya haram nahin hoti mashrub ke haram na honey ki soorat mein un bartanon ko istimal kar saktey ho.)"
3701,"Janab shareek bin Abdullah ne apni sanad se riwayat kya, farmaya : ''jo chiz nasha dey us se ijtinab karo.''"
3702,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye mishkizey mein nabeez banaya jata tha. jab mishkiza na hota to pathar ke badey piyaley mein bana liya kartey they.
3703,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kishmish aur khajoor mila kar nabeez bananey se mana farmaya hai aur aisey hi taza (pukhta) khajoor aur neem pukhta (gadri hui) khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey se roka hai.
3704,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke kishmish aur khajoor (khushk) ko milaana, neem pukhta aur (khushk ( khajoor ko milaana aur naa-pukhta khajoor ( jisney abhi surkh ya zard rang pakda ho (aur taza khajoor ko mila kar nabeez banana mana hai. kaha ke un chizon mein se her eik se alehda alehda taur par nabeez banao . abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ne abu-Qatada se usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki ."
3705,ibne-abi Leila eik sahabi se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kachchi khajoor aur pukhta khajoor aur usi tarah kishmish aur khajoor ko milaaney se mana farmaya hai.
3706,Kabsha binte-abi Maryam kehti hain ke maine ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kis chiz se mana kya kartey they? unhoney kaha : aap hamen mana kartey they ke khajoor ko is qadr pakaeyn ke uski guthli hi khatam ho jaey ya kishmish aur khajoor ko milaaney se mana kartey they.
3707,ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye kishmish ki nabeez banai jati aur phir us mein khajoor dal di jati thi ya khajoor ki nabeez banai jati aur phir us mein kishmish dal di jati thi.
3708,Safiya binte-Atiya kehti hain ke main wafad abdul-Qais ki khawatin ke sath Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaee. ham ne aap se khajoor aur kishmish ko milaney ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : main eik mutthi khajoor aur eik mutthi kishmish leti aur unhen pani mein dal deti phir unhen apney haath se masalti aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh karti aur unhen pilaya karti thi.
3709,Janab Jabir bin Zaid aur Ikrima (Rahimahullah) ke mutalliq aata hai ke wo dono basar (neem pukhta khajoor) ki nabeez ko makruh samajhtey they aur wo ye baat Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bayan kartey they. aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : mujhey andesha hai ke ye wohi (mazaa') na ho jisse Abdul-Qais ke wafad ko mana kiya gaya tha. (Hisham ne kaha : ( maine Qatada se puchha : ''(mazaa') se kya murad hai? to unhoney kaha ke sabz (hara) raughan miley huey ghadey aur raughane-zift (cheed ka gond) lagey bartan mein tayyar karda nabeez ko (mazaa') kehtey hain.
3710,"Janab Abdullah bin (Feeroz) Dailmee apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap jantey hain ke ham kon hain, kahan se aaye hain aur kis ke paas aaye hain? aapney farmaya : ''Allah ki taraf aaye ho aur uskey Rasool ki taraf.'' ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey yahan angoor hotey hain ham unka kya keren? aapney farmaya : ''unhen khushk karkey zubaib yani kishmish bana liya karo.'' ham ne arz kiya : ham (zubaib) kishmish ka kya keren? aapney farmaya : ''subah ke waqt bhigo diya karo aur raat ko pi liya karo.'' aur raat ko bhigo rakha karo aur subah ko pi liya karo aur nabeez mishkeezon mein banaya karo, matkon mein nahin, tehqiq usey nichorne mein jab takheer ho jati hai to ye sirka bin jati hai.''"
3711,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye eik aisey mishkeezey mein nabeez banai jati thi jiskey ooper ke dahaane ko dhaagey se baandh diya jata aur uskey nichey ki taraf surakh they. subah ke waqt bhigoya jata to aap usey Isha ke waqt nosh farma letey aur raat ko bhigoya jata to aap subah ko pi liya kartey.
3712,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye subah ke waqt nabeez bhigo rakhteen. isliye jab shaam hoti aur aap raat ka khana khatey to usey pi letey. agar kuchh bach jata to main usey gira deti thi. phir raat ke waqt bhigo rakhti , jab subah hoti aur aap khana khatey to us waqt pi letey. bayan kiya ke ham mishkeezey ko subah, shaam dhotey they. merey walid (Hayyaan) ne Umra se kaha : kya eik din mein usey do dafa dhoya jata tha? unhoney kaha : haan."
3713,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye kishmish ki nabeez banai jati thi to aap usey us din, agley din aur us se agley din yani teesrey din ki shaam tak istimal kartey they, phir aap hukm detey ke khaadimon ko pila di jaey ya gira di jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke khaadimon ko pilaney se maqsood ye hai ke kharab honey se pehley-pehley usey istimal kar liya jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : sanad mein mazkur Abu-Umar ka naam Yahya bin Ubaid Al Bahraani hai."
3714,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (mamool ke mutabiq azwaaje mutah'raat (biwiyon) ke yahan chakkar lagatey to) Hazrat Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan rukte aur unke yahan se shehad nosh farmaya kartey. to maine aur Hafsa ne aapas mein tey kiya ke ham mein se jiskey paas bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laeyn to wo kahey ke main aap se maghaafeer (jandi ke ras) ki boo mehsoos karti hun. chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein se eik ke paas aaye to usney ye baat keh di. to aapney farmaya : ''(nahin) maine to Zenab ke paas shehad piya hai aur aainda hergiz nahin piyun ga.'' chunanche Sura Tahreem ki ye aayaat nazil ho gaeen. (لِمَ تُحَرِّمُ ما أَحَلَّ اللَّهُ - - - - إِنْ تَتُوبَا إِلَى اللَّهِ) (is ka ( ishara Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf hai aur ( وَإِذْ أَسَرَّ النَّبِيُّ إِلَى بَعْضِ أَزْوَاجِهِ حَدِيثًا ) ''aur jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni eik biwi se raz daraana baat ki.'' to ye raz wohi tha jo aapney kaha tha ke ''balke maine shehad piya hai.''
3715,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko meetha aur shehad bahut pasand tha. . . aur mazkura baala qissey ka kuchh hissey bayan kiya. . . (aur kaha ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat bahut giraan mehsoos hoti thi ke aap se koi nagawar boo aaye. is hadees mein hai ke Hazrat Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : balke aapney maghaafeer (jandi ka ras) piya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(nahin) balke maine to shehad piya hai jo mujhey Hafsa ne pilaya hai.''  to maine kaha : (shayad) shehad ki makkhi ne arfat ka ras choosaa hoga. (arfat) eik buti ka naam hai jis par shehad ki makkhi baithti hai.Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (maghaafeer) eik tarah ki gond si hoti hai. aur (jarast) ke maani hain, , usney choosaa hoga aur (arfat) eik buti hoti hai jis par shehad ki makkhi baithti hai."
3716,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke mujhey ilm tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) roza rakha kartey hain, chunanche (eik roz) mein aap ke liye iftaar ke waqt nabeez ley aaya jo maine kadu ke bartan mein banai thi aur us mein khameer utha hua tha (wo josh maar rahi thi) to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey us deewar par dey maar, bila-shuba ye un logon ka mashrub hai jo Allah aur aakhirat par emaan nahin rakhtay.''"
3717,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi bhi shakhs ko, khadey ho kar peeney se mana farmaya hai."
3718,"Janab Nazzal bin Sabra se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani mangwaya aur khadey ho kar piya, phir kaha : tehqiq kuchh log isko makruh samajhney lagey hain halanke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke is tarah kar liya kartey they jaisey tum ne mujhey kartey dekha hai. (yani khadey ho kar pi liya kartey they.)"
3719,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke mishkeezey ke munh se munh laga kar piya jaey aur gandagi khaney waley janwar par sawari ki jaey aur aisa janwar khaya jaey jis ko baandh kar nishana maara gaya ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : jalaala us janwar ko kehtey hain jo pakhana khata ho. (yani jiski ye aadat ho.)
3720,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya hai ke mishkeezon ka munh ulat kar un se piya jaey.
3721,Esa bin Abdullah Ansari apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke uhud ke din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mishkeeza mangwaya phir farmaya : ''iska munh ultaaoo.'' phir aapney uskey munh se (munh laga kar pani) piya.
3722,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke piyaley ki tooti hui jagah se piya jaey ya mashrub mein phunk maari jaey. Ahmed bin Hazam bayan kartey hain ke hamein Abu-Saeed bin Aa'raabi ne bayan kiya ke mujhey Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) se Qurrat bin Abdur-Rehman bin Hiwel bin Kaasirul Mudd ki baabat ye khabar pahunchi hai ke unhen (کاسرالمد) ''mudd todney wala'' isliye kehtey hain ke eik dafa unhoney badshah ke darbar mein mudd tod diya tha, to usi wajeh se unhen isi naam se pukara janey laga."
3723,"Janab ibne-Abi Leila ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) madaain mein they, unhoney pani talab kiya to eik dahqaan chaandi ke bartan mein pani ley aaya. to unhoney usey phenk maara aur phir kaha : maine isey bilaa wajah nahin phenka balke main usko isse pehley mana kar chuka hun, magar ye baaz nahin aaya. aur tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hareer (resham) aur deebaaj se mana farmaya hai (hareer aam resham aur deebaaj bareek resham ko kehtey hain) aur soney chaandi ke bartanon mein peeney se roka hai aur farmaya hai : ''ye chizen unke liye duniya mein hain aur tumharey liye aakhirat mein.''"
3724,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney eik sahabi ke sath eik Ansari ke yahan tashrif ley gaey jabke wo apney baagh mein pani laga raha tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumharey paas aisa pani hai jo raat bhar mishkeezey mein ho (to ley aao) warna ham kunein ke hauz mein jama shuda pani hi munh laga kar pi letey hain.'' usney kaha : haan , merey paas mishkeezey mein raat ka pani maujud hai."
3725,Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qaum ko pilaney wala sab se aakhir mein piye.''
3726,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko doodh pesh kiya gaya jis mein pani milaayaa gaya tha. aur aap ki daain janib eik dehati tha aur baeyn janib Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they. aapney doodh piya , phir us dehati ko dey diya aur farmaya : ''dahaney wala, phir dahiney wala.''"
3727,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab peetey to teen saans letey aur farmatey : ''ye (andaz) piyas khoob bujhaata hai, hazam ko quwat deta hai aur tandurusti ka baais (wajah) hai.''"
3728,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bartan mein saans leney ya us mein phunk maarney se mana farmaya hai.
3729,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu Anhuma) jo qabeela bani sulaim se hain, unka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey walid ke yahan tashrif laye aur kuchh der thehrey. merey walid ne aap ko khana pesh kiya. unhoney zikr kiya ke wo khana hees (eik khas qism ka khana jo khajoor, paneer, ghi aur aatey waghera ka murakkab hota hai) tha jo laya gaya. phir wo mashrub laye jo aapney nosh farmaya, phir apney daain taraf waley ko dey diya, aur aapney khajuren khaeen aur guthliyaan apni angusht shahadat aur sath wali ungli ki pusht par rakhtey gaey. phir jab aap wahan se uthey to merey walid ne uth kar aap ki sawari ki lagaam thaam li aur arz kiya ke merey liye Allah se dua farmaeyn, to aapney farmaya : (اللهم بارك لهم في رزقتهم , واغفر لهم وارحمهم ) ''aey Allah ! jo to ne inhen inayat farmaya hai is mein inhen barkat dey, inki maghfirat farma aur in par rehmat nazil kar.''"
3730,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain main (apni khaala) Ummul-momenin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur aap ke sath Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. ghar walon ne do saandey bhuney huey pesh kiye jo do lakdiyon par rakhey huey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (unhen dekh kar) thook diya to Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mera khayal hai aap isey napasand kartey hain? aapney farmaya : ''haan'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein doodh pesh kiya gaya jo aapney nosh farma (pee) liya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi khana khaye to yun dua kiya karey (اللهم ! بارك لنا فيه وأطعمنا خيرا منه) ''aey Allah ! hamein is mein barkat dey aur is se umda ata farma.'' aur jab usey doodh pilaya jaey to yun kahey : (اللهم ! بارك لنا فيه وزدنا منه) ''aey Allah ! hamein is mein barkat dey aur mazeed inayat farma.'' doodh ke siwa aur koi aisi chiz nahin hai jo khaney aur peeney dono se kifaayat karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye alfaz Janab Musaddad ke hain.
3731,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apna darwaza band kar aur Allah ka naam ley , bila-shuba shaitan band darwaza nahin khol sakta. apna chiragh bujha aur Allah ka naam ley . apna bartan dhanp kar rakh chahey (chahe) is mein koi lakdi aadey taur par rakh dey aur Allah ka naam ley. aur apney mishkeezey ka tasma baandh kar rakh aur Allah ka naam ley.''"
3732,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki (Abdullah bin Muslima ki) ye riwayat mukammal nahin hai, farmaya : ''shaitan band darwaza nahin khol sakta, na tasma aur bandhna hi khol sakta hai aur na dhaanpey huey bartan ko nanga kar sakta hai, (chiragh bujha kar na soyaa jaey to uska nuqsan ye hai ke) chuhiyaa logon ke gharon ko jala daalti hai.'' (batti ko ghaseet ley jati hai aur is tarah ghar mein aag lag jati hai.)"
3733,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne marfooan bayan kiya : ''Isha ke waqt . . . aur Janab Musaddad ne riwayat kiya ke . . . shaam ke waqt apney bachchon ko (gharon mein) rok kar rakha karo. is waqt jin (zameen mein) phel jatey hain aur (bachchon ko) uchak letey hain.''
3734,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke (eik baar) ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they ke aapney pani talab farmaya, eik shakhs ne kaha : kya ham aap ko nabeez na pesh keren? aapney farmaya : ''kyon nahin.'' chunanche wo bhaagtaa bhaagtaa gaya aur eik piyala ley aaya, us mein nabeez thi , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu ne isey dhanpa kyon nahin? is par koi lakdi hi rakh leta. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (Imame-lughat) Isma'ee ne is lafz ko (تعرضه عليه) padha hai. (راء ke pesh ke sath jabkey doosrey zer se padhtey hain.)"
3735,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye mitha pani ''Saqeeya'' ke gharon se laya jata tha. Quteba ne kaha : ''Saqeeya'' eik chashmey ka naam tha jo Madiney se do din ki masafat (doori) par tha.
